graph.tree.pq

Class PQTree<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.elements.Graph<PQTreeNode,PQTreeEdge>
      • graph.tree.pq.PQTree<V,E>

  • public class PQTree<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
extends Graph<PQTreeNode,PQTreeEdge>
    Tree used in some algorithms for planarity testing P nodes are cut vertices Q nodes are nonseparable components Leaves are virtual vertices (vertices on the other side of edges where one vertex is on subgraph Gk and the other one is in V-Vk)
    Author:
    xx
